{"tid":1126140,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有趣嘅識女仔經歷","createTime":"2019-04-26T07:20:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-26T08:48:32.000Z","uid":111256,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"29e59f99980527d103a5544474803f7a975d7343","tid":1126140,"uid":111256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T07:20:30.000Z","msg":"時下年青人都用交友App或者上網識女仔<br />\n好似冇咗日常生活中相識嘅情趣<br />\n想聽吓啲有趣嘅故事 唔一定要一齊咗都可以分享<br />\n<br />\n我有兩個<br />\n1 - 同成班Friend去打邊爐 見到隔離枱有個好靚嘅鬼妹 靚到好似天使下凡咁<br />\n我昅咗成晚 等到佢嗰枱食完 要走嗰陣 主動行埋去撩佢傾計<br />\n第一句係 &quot;你渣筷子渣得好好喎 可唔可以教我？&quot;<br />\n跟住就識咗 拎咗電話 去咗幾次街<br />\n<br />\n2 - 同幾個Friend去旅行 自己渣車<br />\n離開第一個景點時見到有兩個鬼妹截緊順風車 <br />\n我停低望一望Map 見都幾順路就車埋佢地<br />\n佢地走嗰陣我話 &quot;我同啲朋友聽日去行山 你地可以Join我地&quot;<br />\n之後第二日就一齊行山食飯 玩咗成日 都幾開心<br />\n走嗰陣 佢地話 如果以後去開London可以約佢地<br />\n應該會再見"},{"pid":"c640efad31639ce51db2c160a35ffaec85d7c331","tid":1126140,"uid":243854,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T07:23:03.000Z","msg":"結果兩次都係識完無再理過樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBTW單拖去旅行，咁啱有對香港夫婦一齊玩，之後約咗食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過我無交換聯絡方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce73f62d32129dc11be958d87f71b776ed98c6e0","tid":1126140,"uid":53194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T07:25:26.000Z","msg":"加甜 please"},{"pid":"cd444ebcf799ce599cca0c398f3d1639669b788d","tid":1126140,"uid":79638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce73f62d32129dc11be958d87f71b776ed98c6e0","tid":1126140,"uid":53194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T07:25:26.000Z","msg":"加甜 please"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T08:44:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e214eb63670cd6ac5ae6236d4403f134933051c2","tid":1126140,"uid":218977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T08:46:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8a6b3c5ce2774ce09140811acbb089ba9724ffa9","tid":1126140,"uid":66099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T08:48:32.000Z","msg":"我喺hkcc識大把"}]}